title: Jake Coker has been given a few interesting nicknames from his teammates
text:
Jake Coker has been given a few interesting nicknames from his teammates FOX Sports 
Oct 19, 2015 at 8:03p ET + 
Coker has brought some unexpected elusiveness to the Tide's quarterback position this season. Troy Taormina / USA TODAY Sports FOX Sports   8:03p ET 
When you think of Jacob Coker, what's the first thought that comes to your mind? Considering Nick Saban sat him against Ole Miss in order to get the more athletic Cooper Bateman, you most likely are not envisioning his open field moves. 
Well Coker actually showed off his underrated running ability against Texas A&M last weekend, busting a few runs for quality yardage against the Aggies. For his efforts, Coker has earned a few new nicknames via his teammates: true — Matt Zenitz (@mzenitz) October 19, 2015 true Jake Coker said he has a couple other nicknames too: Vanilla Vick, Cam Cracker. "It's getting out of hand," he said. — Ben Jones (@BW_Jones) October 19, 2015 
Tennessee had best be on high alert when they travel to Tuscaloosa this Saturday, you never want to get beat by a guy nicknamed Vanilla Vick. MORE NEWS: Want stories delivered to you? Sign up for our College Football newsletters.
